kind of like him, too.

31
00:02:53,725 --> 00:02:54,840
But

32
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,520
we've been friends for years.

33
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:57,880
So I just

34
00:02:58,325 --> 00:02:59,920
don't know how to do.

35
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:02,960
Jian Dan,

36
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:05,840
