37
00:03:09,245 --> 00:03:10,131
It's Sheng.

38
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:15,040
Do you know why everyone calls him Han,

39
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:17,080
but I'm the only one
who calls him Sheng?

40
00:03:18,925 --> 00:03:21,080
It's because I saved his life once.

41
00:03:22,542 --> 00:03:24,160
And ever since then,

42
00:03:24,885 --> 00:03:26,674
