125
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,360
Look.

126
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:23,000
Yuan Sen studies art.

127
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:25,897
He turns knowledge into comics.

128
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,960
