279
00:19:44,080 --> 00:19:44,840
Mi Fen.

280
00:19:45,760 --> 00:19:47,440
Let me ask you something.

281
00:19:50,240 --> 00:19:52,080
I just met with Han Yansheng.

282
00:19:53,280 --> 00:19:54,440
He told me

