00:32:24,560 --> 00:32:25,388
the pool is huge.

570
00:32:25,417 --> 00:32:27,720
Can we finish it in half a day?

571
00:32:28,410 --> 00:32:29,844
It's 800 yuan for half a day's work.

572
00:32:29,920 --> 00:32:31,040
That's a great deal.

573
00:32:31,354 --> 00:32:32,200
Stop complaining.

574
00:32:33,520 --> 00:32:34,857
Yeah.

575
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:37,000
But still,

576
00:32:37,108 --> 00:32:38,240
why would Han Yansheng

577
00:32:38,280 --> 00:32:39,600
give us this job?

578
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:42,880
Maybe the pool really needs cleaning.

579
00:32:43,468 --> 00:32:45,000
Look how dirty the floor is.

580
00:32:45,480 --> 00:32:47,440
No one's cleaned in it for ages.

581
00:32:48,320 --> 00:32:49,640
Exactly.

582
00:32:49,988 --> 00:32:51,160
I told you.

583
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:52,297
With this workload,

584
00:32:52,320 --> 00:32:54,109
Han Yansheng is definitely
not losing out.

585
00:32:54,110 --> 00:32:55,200
He's too smart

586
00:32:55,234 --> 00:32:57,160
to do something so dumb.

587
00:32:57,760 --> 00:32:59,017
Enough chatting.

588
00:32:59,080 --> 00:33:00,040
Hurry and work.

589
00:33:00,160 --> 00:33:01,760
If he catches us slacking,

590
00:33:01,800 --> 00:33:03,466
we'll be in trouble.

591
00:33:20,120 --> 00:33:21,417
Here's your payment.

592
00:33:23,600 --> 00:33:24,800
Let me be clear.

593
00:33:25,560 --> 00:33:27,577
If you didn't urgently need the money,

594
00:33:27,640 --> 00:33:29,720
I would've hired professionals instead.

595
00:33:30,280 --> 00:33:31,840
I believe they're faster

596
00:33:31,933 --> 00:33:33,240
and probably do a better job.

597
00:33:35,840 --> 00:33:36,520
Thanks.

598
00:33:38,360 --> 00:33:39,200
Great.

599
00:33:39,760 --> 00:33:41,560
We've got money for the rent.

600
00:33:41,560 --> 00:33:42,160
Let's go.

601
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:43,880
Thank you, President.

602
00:33:58,920 --> 00:33:59,680
Sheng,

603
00:33:59,920 --> 00:34:01,280
I heard you had Jian Dan and Mi Fen

604
00:34:01,280 --> 00:34:02,560
clean the pool.

605
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:04,160
I'll deduct the cleaning fee

606
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:05,800
from our club budget.

607
00:34:06,360 --> 00:34:06,800
No need.

608
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:08,640
I paid for it personally.

609
00:34:08,688 --> 00:34:10,155
It has nothing to do with the club.

610
00:34:14,960 --> 00:34:16,520
Come. This is done. Hang it up.

611
00:34:16,520 --> 00:34:17,080
Here you go.

612
00:34:18,480 --> 00:34:19,160
Okay.

613
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:22,800
Look at this.

614
00:34:23,360 --> 00:34:24,800
What do I do with this?

615
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:29,000
I'll pull it.

616
00:34:50,520 --> 00:34:51,280
I'm heading off.

617
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:54,480
Dismissed.

618
00:35:02,480 --> 00:35:05,680
(Shi, is there an event
at the coffee shop today?)

619
00:35:08,600 --> 00:35:10,640
(Shi: Jian Dan is confessing there.)

620
00:35:15,160 --> 00:35:17,800
(Why did Shi send the photo
to Sheng?)

621
00:35:19,360 --> 00:35:22,520
(Is Sheng the one she's confessing to?)

622
00:35:27,640 --> 00:35:28,800
Everything's set up, right?

623
00:35:29,088 --> 00:35:29,960
I'll get going then.

624
00:35:30,088 --> 00:35:31,400
Good luck with your confession.

625
00:35:33,440 --> 00:35:34,400
Thank you, Shi.

626
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:39,120
He was talking to me, right?

627
00:35:43,200 --> 00:35:44,311
Jian Dan, it's almost time.

628
00:35:44,311 --> 00:35:46,000
I need to go back to the dorm
and change.

629
00:35:46,000 --> 00:35:47,000
I'll leave this to you.

630
00:35:47,000 --> 00:35:48,150
Don't worry. I've got this...

631
00:35:49,680 --> 00:35:50,960
Jian Dan.

632
00:36:15,720 --> 00:36:16,960
You're back already?

633
00:36:18,240 --> 00:36:18,920
I came early?

634
00:36:22,120 --> 00:36:23,244
What are you doing here?

635
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:25,180
Who did you think it would be?

636
00:36:26,920 --> 00:36:27,720
Since you're here,

637
00:36:27,720 --> 00:36:28,760
give me a hand.

638
00:36:31,560 --> 00:36:32,800
(Did she write her confession)

639
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:34,200
(inside the paper crane?)

640
00:36:34,377 --> 00:36:35,720
(That's so cliche.)

641
00:36:43,440 --> 00:36:44,555
Why is there nothing inside?

642
00:36:46,960 --> 00:36:49,200
Maybe this one?

643
00:36:50,400 --> 00:36:51,440
I just folded them.

644
00:36:51,440 --> 00:36:52,880
Why did you open them all?

645
00:36:54,640 --> 00:36:55,400
You.

646
00:36:56,222 --> 00:36:57,511
Go rest over there.

647
00:37:53,684 --> 00:37:57,134
♪Suddenly the street view feels familiar♪

648
00:37:57,874 --> 00:38:01,344
♪Memories come too abruptly♪

649
00:38:02,814 --> 00:38:06,194
♪It feels nothing,
yet they come back time after time♪

650
00:38:07,084 --> 00:38:10,404
♪Where should I begin♪

651
00:38:11,154 --> 00:38:14,644
♪To reach back to that time?♪

652
00:38:15,994 --> 00:38:19,054
♪A certain look, a certain lyric♪

653
00:38:19,384 --> 00:38:25,094
♪Before I even start reminiscing,
my eyes are already wet♪

654
00:38:26,194 --> 00:38:29,974
♪It feels like a lifetime ago♪

655
00:38:30,344 --> 00:38:34,104
♪Those youthful little things♪

656
00:38:34,104 --> 00:38:37,054
♪Ordinary, yet meaningful♪

657
00:38:37,364 --> 00:38:43,014
♪Quietly speeding
through the cracks of time♪

658
00:38:43,684 --> 00:38:47,354
♪Those scattered past memories♪

659
00:38:47,844 --> 00:38:50,114
♪Names now blurred♪

660
00:38:50,374 --> 00:38:58,004
♪Thankfully, we once had each other♪

661
00:39:00,344 --> 00:39:03,974
♪Those youthful little things♪

662
00:39:03,974 --> 00:39:07,154
♪Heartbeats that needed no disguise♪

663
00:39:07,464 --> 00:39:13,094
♪When someday, promises became a luxury♪

664
00:39:13,664 --> 00:39:17,184
♪Those scattered past memories♪

665
00:39:17,444 --> 00:39:20,164
♪Were never truly lost♪

666
00:39:20,344 --> 00:39:27,994
♪They form the complete blueprint
of a colorful life♪
